import React from 'react'
import Hero from './Hero'
import Info from './Info'
import LinkForm from './LinkForm'

const Main = ({onSubmit, changeHandler, value, links}) => {
    return(
        <main className="main-content">
            <Hero/>
            <LinkForm onSubmit={onSubmit} changeHandler={changeHandler} value={value}/>
            <Info links={links} />
        </main>
    )
}

export default Main
